<p>To promote meaningful debate and public awareness about immigration, deportation and exile, we will be giving away copies of the &lt;/em&gt;<em><strong><a href="http://amzn.to/11dNDPd" target="_self">Amor and Exile</a></strong></em> free Kindle book on Thursday and Friday of this week!</p>

<p>Our Kindle version can be read on almost  <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/feature.html?docId=1000493771">any computer, tablet or smartphone</a>, not just on Kindles.</p>

